      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your<strong> steak</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it adjust to room temperature</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and finely dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s] </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and finely dice</p>",
