    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, pat the <strong>pork loin steak[s] </strong>dry with kitchen paper and season both sides with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>spice</strong> <strong>mix </strong>(save the rest for later!)</p>",
